ational who had returned from Italy.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.indiatoday.in/india/story/coronavirus-india-outbreak-fresh-case-news-update-delhi-telangana-1651586-2020-03-02|title=Two fresh cases of coronavirus detected in India; one in Delhi, another in Telangana|website=India Today|date=2 March 2020|access-date=2 March 2020}}</ref> Later the same day, an Italian tourist who had arrived in [[Jaipur]], Rajasthan on 29 February tested positive in a second test after having previously tested negative.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/india/coronavirus-live-updates-south-korea-reports-476-new-cases-total-at-4212/liveblog/74432985.cms|title=Coronavirus India Live Updates: Italian tests positive for coronavirus in Jaipur|website=The Times of India|access-date=2 March 2020}}</ref> On 3 March, his wife also tested positive.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.businesstoday.in/current/economy-politics/coronavirus-outbreak-case-live-updates-latest-news-covid-19-delhi-noida-agra-india/story/397426.html|title=Coronavirus Live Updates: Italian tourist's wife tests positive, number of cases rises to 7|website=Business Today|date=3 March 2020|access-date=3 March 2020}}</ref>\nOn 4 March 14 more Italian tourists who were kept at a quarantine facility in Delhi were confirmed positive, as well as the group's Indian driver.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/politics-and-nation/28-confirmed-cases-of-coronavirus-in-india-gom-to-meet-today-health-minister-harsh-vardhan/articleshow/74472369.cms|title=28 confirmed cases of coronavirus in India, GoM to meet today: Health minister Harsh Vardhan|date=4 March 2020|work=The Economic Times|access-date=4 March 2020}}</ref> A [[Paytm]] employee in [[Gurgaon]] who had returned from a vacation in Italy also tested positive.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.indiatoday.in/india/story/coronavirus-covid19-paytm-employee-tests-positive-gurugram-1652475-2020-03-04|title=29th coronavirus case in India: After 15 Italian tourists, Paytm employee tests positive for Covid-19|last=DelhiMarch 4|first=Aishwarya Paliwal New|last2=March 5|first2=2020UPDATED|website=India Today|access-date=8 March 2020|last3=Ist|first3=2020 13:52}}</ref> On 8 March, five members of a family in [[Kerala]] tested positive, three of whom had returned from Italy.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ndtv.com/india-news/5-of-family-infected-with-coronavirus-in-kerala-total-positive-cases-in-india-rise-to-39-2191757|title=5 Of Family in Kerala Get Coronavirus, 39 Cases in India: 10 Points|website=NDTV.com|access-date=8 March 2020}}</ref>\n\n'''Israel''' \u2013\nOn 27 February, Israel confirmed that a man who had returned from Italy on 23 February tested positive and was admitted to [[Sheba Medical Center]] at [[Tel HaShomer]].<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/israeli-who-visited-italy-tests-positive-for-coronavirus-1.8594185|title=Israeli Who Visited Italy Tests Positive for Coronavirus|date=27 February 2020|work=Haaretz|access-date=27 February 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.i24news.tv/en/news/israel/diplomacy-defense/1582799308-israeli-who-returned-from-italy-diagnosed-with-coronavirus-ministry|title=Israeli who returned from Italy diagnosed with coronavirus: ministry|website=i24 News|date=27 February 2020|access-date=27 February 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ynetnews.com/article/SkMzcIBV8|title=El Al suspends all flights to Italy and Thailand over coronavirus fears|date=27 February 2020|website=Ynet|access-date=27 February 2020}}</ref> On 28 February, his wife also tested positive.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.jpost.com/Breaking-News/Health-Ministry-confirms-second-case-of-coronavirus-in-Israel-619189|title=Health Ministry confirms second case of coronavirus in Israel|website=The Jerusalem Post|date=28 February 2020|access-date=28 February 2020}}</ref>\n\n'''Japan''' \u2013\nOn 13 March, Japan confirmed that a man in his 30s who had been living in Italy since 6 January tested positive for coronavirus upon landing at [[Haneda Airport]] in Tokyo that day. He is currently under quarantine at a hospital in Tokyo.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.asahi.com/articles/ASN3F6D1GN3FULBJ00N.html|title=\u30a4\u30bf\u30ea\u30a2\u304b\u3089\u306e\u5e30\u56fd\u8005\u3001\u521d\u306e\u30b3\u30ed\u30ca\u611f\u67d3\u78ba\u8a8d\u3000\u90fd\u5185\u3067\u5165\u9662 (\"Returnee from Italy tests positive for coronavirus; in hospital in Tokyo\")|language=Japanese|work=Asahi Shimbun|date=13 March 2020|access-date=20 March 2020}}</ref>\n\n'''Jordan''' \u2013\nOn 2 March, Jordan confirmed that a man in his 30s who had returned from Italy two weeks earlier had tested positive, with other potential cases under observation.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://arab.news/v47zf|title=Jordan announces first coronavirus case from Italy|date=2 March 2020|website=Arab News|access-date=5 March 2020}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|author=Zehra Nur D\u00fcz |url=https://www.aa.com.tr/en/health/jordan-confirms-first-coronavirus-case/1752064|title=Jordan confirms first coronavirus case|publisher=Anadolu Agency|date=2 March 2020|access-date=5 March 2020}}</ref>\n\n'''[[Mainland China]]''' \u2013\nOn 1 March, [[Qingtian County]], [[Lishui]], Zhejiang confirmed its first imported case, a 31-year-old Chinese woman who had worked at a restaurant in [[Bergamo]].<ref>{{cite web |script-title=zh:\u4e3d\u6c34\u65b0\u589e1\u4f8b\u610f\u5927\u5229\u8f93\u5165\u6027\u786e\u8bca\u75c5\u4f8b\uff1a31\u5c81\u9752\u7530\u5973\u5b50\u4ece\u610f\u5927\u5229\u5230\u8fbe\u4e0a\u6d77\u6d66\u4e1c\u673a\u573a |url=https://hznews.hangzhou.com.cn/kejiao/content/2020-03/02/content_7686772.htm |language=zh-cn |website=hangzhou.com.cn |date=2 March 2020|access-date=2 March 2020}}</ref> On 2 March, seven more imported cases were confirmed in Qingtian County that are related to the first imported case.<ref>{{cite web |script-title=zh:\u6d59\u6c5f\u9752\u7530\u53bf\u65b0\u589e7\u4f8b\u5883\u5916\u8f93\u51