ople Pleaser\n| RTitle={{Efn|This episode was released online on December 1, 2016.}}\n| WrittenBy=Jaydeep Hasrajani and Leticia Abreu Silva\n| Aux2=Jake Goldman and Haley Mancini\n| OriginalAirDate={{Start date|2016|12|1}}\n| Viewers=1.02<ref>{{Cite web|last=Metcalf|first=Mitch|date=December 28, 2016|url=http://www.showbuzzdaily.com/articles/showbuzzdailys-top-150-saturday-cable-originals-network-finals-12-24-2016.html|title=Top 150 Saturday Cable Originals & Network Finals: December 24, 2016|work=Showbuzz Daily|accessdate=December 28, 2016}}</ref>\n| ShortSummary=Blossom neglects her promise to help Bubbles with her biome project when she takes on too many things leaving Buttercup and Bubbles to fend for themselves, but they inadvertently turn the biome into a giant monster.\n| LineColor=9FDFDF\n}}\n}}<!--Do not delete this line. You will break the table.-->\n\n===Season 2 (2017\u201318)===\n{{Episode table\n| background=#DF9F9F\n| overall=\n| season=\n| title=\n| titleT=Title\n| titleR=\n| writer=\n| writerT=Written and storyboarded by\n| aux2=\n| aux2T=Story by\n| airdate=\n| airdateT=Original air date\n| airdateR=\n| viewers=\n| country=US\n| episodes=\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber=40<hr/>41\n| EpisodeNumber2=1<hr/>2\n| Title=The Last Donnycorn\n| WrittenBy=Kyle Neswald, Benjamin P. Carow,<br />Julia Vickerman, and Cheyenne Curtis\n| Aux2=Jake Goldman and Haley Mancini\n| OriginalAirDate={{Start date|2017|3|3}}\n| Viewers=0.95<ref>[http://www.showbuzzdaily.com/articles/showbuzzdailys-top-150-friday-cable-originals-network-finals-3-3-2017.html \"UPDATED:  SHOWBUZZDAILY\u2019s Top 150 Friday Cable Originals & Network Finals: 3.3.2017 | Showbuzz Daily\"]. ''www.showbuzzdaily.com''. Retrieved on May 31, 2017.</ref>\n| ShortSummary='''Part One:''' When Donny the Unicorn is hunted by a seemingly unstoppable foe, the Powerpuff Girls have to find a way to save him before it's too late.\n----\n'''Part Two:''' In the magical land of unicorns, the Powerpuff Girls and Do