illains an enticing offer.\n| LineColor=#C8A2C8\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber=110\n| EpisodeNumber2=28\n| Title=The Spoon\n| RTitle=\n| WrittenBy=Kyle Neswald and Jaydeep Hasrajani\n| Aux2=Jake Goldman \n| OriginalAirDate={{Start date|2019|3|31}}\n| Viewers=0.37<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.showbuzzdaily.com/articles/showbuzzdailys-top-150-sunday-cable-originals-network-finals-3-31-2019.html|title=Top 150 Sunday Cable Originals and Network Finals: 3.31.2019|author=Mitch Metcalf|work=Showbuzz Daily|date=April 2, 2019|accessdate=April 2, 2019}}</ref>\n| ShortSummary=A crash landing sends Townsville over the edge.\n| LineColor=#C8A2C8\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber=111\n| EpisodeNumber2=29\n| Title=Cat Burglar\n| RTitle=\n| WrittenBy=Benjamin P. Carow and Caitlin Vanarsdale\n| Aux2=Haley Mancini\n| OriginalAirDate={{Start date|2019|4|7}}\n| Viewers=0.39<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.showbuzzdaily.com/articles/showbuzzdailys-top-150-sunday-cable-originals-network-finals-4-7-2019.html|title=Top 150 Sunday Cable Originals and Network Finals: 4.7.2019|author=Mitch Metcalf|work=Showbuzz Daily|date=April 9, 2019|accessdate=April 9, 2019}}</ref>\n| ShortSummary=An alarmingly familiar cat burglar terrorizes Townsville.\n| LineColor=#C8A2C8\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber=112\n| EpisodeNumber2=30\n| Title=Hustlecup\n| RTitle=\n| WrittenBy=Kyle Neswald and Jaydeep Hasrajani\t\n| Aux2=Jake Goldman\n| OriginalAirDate={{Start date|2019|4|7}}\n| Viewers=0.39<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.showbuzzdaily.com/articles/showbuzzdailys-top-150-sunday-cable-originals-network-finals-4-7-2019.html|title=Top 150 Sunday Cable Originals and Network Finals: 4.7.2019|author=Mitch Metcalf|work=Showbuzz Daily|date=April 9, 2019|accessdate=April 9, 2019}}</ref>\n| ShortSummary=When Buttercup loses the Professor\u2019s latest invention, she\u2019ll have to beat The Gangreen Gang at their own game to get it back.\n| LineColor=#C8A2C8\n}}\n{{Episode list\n| EpisodeNumber=113\n| Episod