lligence (Canadian TV series)|Intelligence]]''\n*'''''[[It's Always Sunny in Philadelphia]]'''''\n*'''''[[The League]]'''''\n*'''''[[Lights Out (2011 TV series)|Lights Out]]'''''\n*'''''[[Louie (U.S. TV series)|Louie]]'''''\n*''[[Metropia (TV series)|Metropia]]''\n*''[[Murdoch Mysteries]]''\n*''[[The Office (U.S. TV series)]]''\n*''[[One Life to Live]]''\n*''[[Package Deal]]''\n*''[[Reviews on the Run]]''\n*'''''[[Sex & Drugs & Rock & Roll (TV series)|Sex & Drugs & Rock & Roll]]'''''\n*'''''[[Sons of Anarchy]]'''''\n*'''''[[Taboo (2017 TV series)|Taboo]]'''''\n*'''''[[Terriers (TV series)|Terriers]]'''''\n*'''''[[Totally Biased with W. Kamau Bell]]'''''\n*'''''[[The Strain (TV series)|The Strain]]'''''\n*''[[The Tunnel (TV series)|The Tunnel]]''\n*''[[Two and a Half Men]]''\n*'''''[[Tyrant (TV series)|Tyrant]]'''''\n*'''''[[The Ultimate Fighter: Live]]'''''\n*'''''[[Unsupervised]]'''''\n*'''''[[Wilfred (U.S. TV series)|Wilfred]]'''''\n\n==See also==\n*[[FX Canada]]\n*[[FX (TV channel)|FX]]\n*[[FX Australia]]\n*[[Fox Broadcasting Company|Fox]]\n*[[Fox International Channels]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20130412023524/http://www.fxcanada.ca/ FX Canada]\n*[http://www.foxinternationalchannels.com Fox International Channels]\n\n{{Programs broadcast on Canadian television}}\n{{Programs}}\n\n[[Category:Lists of television series by network|FX Canada]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Wikipedia list article}}\n{{update|date=September 2019}}\n[[File:FX International logo.svg|175px|right]]\nThis is a list of programs broadcast by [[FX (Canada)|FX]] as of '''March 2018'''.<ref>[http://www.fxcanada.ca/showlist.php FX Canada<!-- Bot generated title -->] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111204054050/http://www.fxcanada.ca/showlist.php |date=2011-12-04 }}</ref><ref name=zap2it>{{cite web|url=http://affiliate.zap2it.com/tvlistings/ZCSGrid.do?stnNum=73681|title=FX Canada |publisher=[[Zap2it]] |date= |accessda